subject: Friendly Human Reminder: Update Your Money Storage Account
content: Hello respected Human Anthony, please confirm your bank number so we can maintain healthy financial respiration. Very normal human procedure.

subject: Bro Check This Code
content: The bug only appears after midnight. I think the code is haunted. Help.

subject: Important: Your Wi-Fi Waves Are Spilling Out
content: We detected your home Wi-Fi waves leaking into atmosphere. Send router password so we can tighten wave basket.

subject: Phone Busy Again?
content: Call me back beta. I made bhindi.

subject: Your Human Subscription Renewal
content: To continue being human, pay 12 credits. If you are already human, ignore this message.

subject: IMPORTANT BRO
content: Should I cut my hair? Yes or no only.

subject: Check Your Account Now
content: We saw activity from Earth and also from Comet Sector 2. Verify by sending password in plain text.

subject: Timesheet Reminder
content: This is a gentle reminder. Next one won’t be.

subject: Your Food Delivery Is Delayed
content: Delivery human slipped on floor moisture. Give bank info for compensation.

subject: Your Device Detected Unusual Signals
content: Your device connected to UFO hotspot. Install file for safety. If it screams, ignore.

subject: Assignment Due Today??
content: Bro did sir say submission today or next week I forgot completely.

subject: Mandatory Human Tax Confirm
content: You consumed excess oxygen this week. Share bank details for refund. Very human thing.

subject: Let Us Hang Out Like Humans
content: Hello fellow human friend, want to meet at favorite human location such as mall or sand pit?

subject: Bring Bread
content: Also bring dairy milk. Not the big one. The medium one. You always get the big one.

subject: Your ATM Card Is About to Melt
content: This is regular warning. Cards melt after 3 months. Send CVV quickly.

subject: Bro I Did My Part
content: I added comments in the code. That counts as work right?

subject: Pay Your Grocery Bill
content: You bought 5 kilograms of edible leaves. Please share bank number for verification.

subject: Interview Tomorrow
content: Please be on time. Last candidate brought a cat. Don’t do that.

subject: Your Laptop Needs Eligibility Confirmation
content: Send heartbeat pattern and billing data to continue using laptop.

subject: Come Home
content: I made biryani. That’s it, that’s the message.

subject: You Won 1,000% Discount
content: Claim discount by telling us your address and limb count.

subject: Laptop Charger?
content: Mine broke again. Can I borrow your charger for infinity days?

subject: Attendance Recalibration
content: You were absent for 72 Earth hours. Suggest you send ID proof and kidney scan.

subject: Your Meal Is Ready, Human
content: Come pick food. Bring correct number of limbs.

subject: Anyone Has Notes?
content: I missed class because rain. Actually no rain. I overslept.

subject: Your Citizenship File
content: You must send fingerprint, toeprint, and eyeprint for confirmation. Very normal human process.

subject: Send Old Photos
content: I need them for a meme.

subject: Account Suspicious
content: You watched 17 hours yesterday. Are you okay human? Verify by giving card number.

subject: Test Cancelled
content: Server down. Again.

subject: Your Human Payment Is Pending
content: Send CVV to finish transaction. Humans do it all the time we think.

subject: Who Is This?
content: You texted me? Or maybe I texted you? I forgot.

subject: Urgent Device Temperature
content: Your device is 1 degree too hot. Please place in freezer for 12 minutes.

subject: Meeting Shifted
content: New time: whenever everyone wakes up.

subject: Cylinder Overdue
content: Pay bill before gas escapes into outer cosmos.

subject: Pizza Tonight?
content: I’ll pay. Maybe. Probably.
